#. <section class="sutta" id="sn43.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn43.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 43"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 43"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn43.11:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 11. Maggaṅgasutta → maggena (pts1)
msgctxt "sn43.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Maggaṅgasutta"
msgstr "11. The Path"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn43.11:1.1"
msgid "“Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo?"
msgstr "“And what is the path that leads to the unconditioned?"

msgctxt "sn43.11:1.2"
msgid "Ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo."
msgstr "The noble eightfold path."

msgctxt "sn43.11:1.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo."
msgstr "This is called the path that leads to the unconditioned."

msgctxt "sn43.11:1.4"
msgid ""
"Iti kho, bhikkhave, desitaṃ vo mayā asaṅkhataṃ, desito asaṅkhatagāmimaggo."
msgstr ""
"So, mendicants, I’ve taught you the unconditioned and the path that leads to "
"the unconditioned."

msgctxt "sn43.11:1.5"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, bhikkhave, satthārā karaṇīyaṃ sāvakānaṃ hitesinā anukampakena anukampaṃ "
"upādāya kataṃ vo taṃ mayā."
msgstr ""
"Out of compassion, I’ve done what a teacher should do who wants what’s best "
"for their disciples."

msgctxt "sn43.11:1.6"
msgid ""
"Etāni, bhikkhave, rukkhamūlāni, etāni suññāgārāni. Jhāyatha, bhikkhave, mā "
"pamādattha; mā pacchā vippaṭisārino ahuvattha. Ayaṃ vo amhākaṃ anusāsanī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Here are these roots of trees, and here are these empty huts. Practice "
"absorption, mendicants! Don’t be negligent! Don’t regret it later! This is "
"my instruction to you.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn43.11:1.7"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn43.11:1.8"
msgid "Asaṅkhatasaṃyuttassa paṭhamo vaggo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn43.11:2.1"
msgid "Kāyo samatho savitakko,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn43.11:2.2"
msgid "suññato satipaṭṭhānā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn43.11:2.3"
msgid "Sammappadhānā iddhipādā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn43.11:2.4"
msgid "indriyabalabojjhaṅgā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn43.11:2.5"
msgid "Maggena ekādasamaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn43.11:2.6"
msgid "tassuddānaṃ pavuccati."
msgstr ""
